sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as Operator / Console
  participant API as Go API
  participant Context as Decision context builder
  participant Gov as Governance engine
  participant LLM as LLM provider
  participant Review as Review service
  participant Outbox as Outbox
  participant Worker as Dispatch worker
  participant Channel as Feishu / GitHub
  participant Audit as Audit log

  User->>API: Create or evaluate decision case
  API->>Context: Load ontology objects, metrics, history, policies
  Context->>Gov: Check thresholds, roles, and action policy
  Gov-->>Context: Constraints and allowed actions
  Context->>LLM: Prompt with grounded operational context
  alt LLM unavailable or disabled
    LLM-->>Context: Rule-based decision
  else LLM available
    LLM-->>Context: Recommendation, confidence, evidence, actions
  end
  Context->>Review: Persist proposal and approval requirements
  Review->>Audit: Record decision trace
  User->>API: Approve / execute proposal
  API->>Outbox: Create dispatchable event
  Worker->>Outbox: Claim due events
  Worker->>Channel: Dispatch action
  Channel-->>Worker: Delivery result
  Worker->>Outbox: Mark sent or retry
  Worker->>Audit: Record operational outcome
